description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;The Corona virus is having an unprecedented impact on the NHS. We need help with general support. &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;If you have experienced a downturn in work and need some additional paid work or just want to do your bit to support the NHS then we want to hear from you!&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Duties may include;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;General social interaction with patients, talking, observing and escalating concerns&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;Cleaning&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;Food preparation and service&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;Housekeeping duties i.e. making beds, filling water jugs&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;Meeting and greeting&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;Putting away stock&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;Carrying out other duties our trained and experienced staff need completing&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;To report any concerns or issues to the manager in charge&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;You could receive a worker assignment through our recruitment process and will receive weekly pay and paid training.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Full and part time hours available.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To get on-board, contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email: cft.flexiteam@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Call: 01208 834664&lt;/p&gt;
